videos.headline: Wadley busts loose for 75-yard Iowa TD
videos.description: Iowa strikes first when Akrum Wadley gets through the line with a sweet juke move and has nothing but green in front of him as he goes 75 yards to the house for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Iowa strikes again for another big-play TD
videos.description: So much for Iowa's lethargic offense, as with a 75-yard touchdown already on the board, the Hawkeyes strike again with a 77-yard touchdown pass from C.J. Beathard to Riley McCarron for a 13-0 lead.

videos.headline: Iowa rips off another long run
videos.description: LeShun Daniels Jr. run for 57-yards to the Neb 7 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Iowa extends lead with 4-yard TD run
videos.description: LeShun Daniels Jr. run for 4 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Nebraska receiver lays out to make great catch
videos.description: Tommy Armstrong Jr. pass complete to Brandon Reilly for 16-yards to the Neb 36 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Iowa opens second half with another TD
videos.description: Iowa's offense has been rolling against Nebraska and strikes again when C.J. Beathard finds George Kittle who just barely breaks the plane to score for the Hawkeyes.

videos.headline: Nebraska scores on 4th down try to cut into Iowa lead
videos.description: Tommy Armstrong Jr. pass complete to Stanley Morgan Jr. for 13-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Iowa scores again on Beathard's third TD pass
videos.description: C.J. Beathard finds George Kittle on the crossing route, Kittle's second of the game and Beathard's third passing touchdown, to boost Iowa's lead to 33-10.

videos.headline: LeShun Daniels gets second rushing TD to extend Iowa lead further
videos.description: LeShun Daniels Jr. run for 1-yard for a TD
